cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is about comparing different supervised classifiers for pattern recognition, which is a common topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other possible categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
